<SYNC Start=1793460><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1793460><P><BR>Fine.
<SYNC Start=1794539><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1794539><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1796540><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1796540><P><BR>Get a lot written today?
