<SYNC Start=1798059><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1804740><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1804740><P><BR>The weather forecast<BR>said it's going to snow tonight.
<SYNC Start=1807339><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1807339><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1811980><P><BR>
