<SYNC Start=1826979><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1830340><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1830340><P><BR>Okay. I understand.
<SYNC Start=1832860><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1832860><P><BR>I'll come back later<BR>with a couple of sandwiches.
