<SYNC Start=1837899><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1837899><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1840900><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1840900><P><BR>Wendy...
<SYNC Start=1842260><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1842260><P><BR>...let me explain something to you.
<SYNC Start=1844739><P><BR>
