<SYNC Start=1855859><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1855859><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1859300><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1859300><P><BR>Fine.
<SYNC Start=1860419><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1860419><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1861500><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1861500><P><BR>We're making a new rule:
<SYNC Start=1863380><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1863380><P><BR>Whenever I'm in here...
