<SYNC Start=1867139><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1867139><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1868820><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1868820><P><BR>...or whatever the fuck<BR>you hear me doing in here...
<SYNC Start=1871860><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1871860><P><BR>...when I'm in here,<BR>that means I am working.
