<SYNC Start=1874260><P><BR>That means don't come in.
<SYNC Start=1876620><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1876620><P><BR>Do you think you can handle that?
<SYNC Start=1878739><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1878739><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1883220><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1883220><P><BR>Fine.
<SYNC Start=1884339><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1884339><P>&nbsp;
<SYNC Start=1885300><P><BR>
<SYNC Start=1885300><P><BR>Why don't you start right now<BR>and get the fuck out of here?
<SYNC Start=1888459><P><BR>
